{"tid":1965880,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇用過tox加密即時通訊軟件取代Telegarm？","createTime":"2020-04-09T18:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T05:46:12.000Z","uid":163841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5c87451446f85e5c555c1620d35d1a22e60c7bd5","tid":1965880,"uid":163841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T18:32:43.000Z","msg":"tox<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tox\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FTox&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVXHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=05aa5621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tox</a><br />\n<br />\n下載<br />\n<a href=\"https://tox.chat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftox.chat%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVXHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=48edf7f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tox.chat/</a><br />\n<br />\nTox是一個使用端到端加密法及對等網路的即時通訊和影片電話協定，遵循GNU通用公眾授權條款協定釋出。該專案的目標是為所有人提供安全而方便的通信方式[1]。此協定的一個參考實現已作為自由及開放原始碼軟體釋出。<br />\n<br />\nTox用戶將會分配到一個公鑰和一個私鑰，之後直接通過一個分散式對等網路互相連接。用戶可以通過Tox給朋友傳送資訊、語音或進行影片聊天，群聊或傳送檔案。所有通過Tox的流量將使用NaCl進行端到端加密。<br />\n<br />\n無中心無法監控"},{"pid":"a1391b335b03e98ee9191a6b88d6da514017738a","tid":1965880,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T19:34:43.000Z","msg":"tg delete 功能垃圾死穴嚟，除非經常delete account 無法破解。"},{"pid":"15aed08a313af721e5951aca91d66305d81faccc","tid":1965880,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"仲有個叫open source app叫Signal<br />\n連backend都open source埋<br />\nsuppose安全過tg<br />\n不過未試過用"},{"pid":"0ae6696d01b53e1c14aeb0b0262469c46d7136e3","tid":1965880,"uid":163841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"15aed08a313af721e5951aca91d66305d81faccc","tid":1965880,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"仲有個叫open source app叫Signal<br />\n連backend都open source埋<br />\nsuppose安全過tg<br />\n不過未試過用"},